---
title: Seared Salmon & Couscous Tabbouleh with Lemon Yoghurt & Roasted Seeds
description: Couscous tabbouleh is a winning side dish – it’s fast, fresh and full of flavour. Serve it next to gently seared salmon and a lemon yoghurt, plus add a sprinkling of roasted seeds for extra goodness and crunch. This meal is a star performer!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c468b5ce3f33973777e0d82-43d91e8b.jpg
